Example of segmentation fault error
===================================

This is an example of a segmentation fault error.
It also shows how memory can be corrupted by writing elements of and 
array that it is out of bounds.

Two compilations available
* compile.sh : Compilation with out any extra flags
* compile_with_debug.sh : Compilation with debug flags

IMPORTANT!
----------

This error is compiler dependent!. The executable compiled using gfortran it is included.

* segmentation_fault : Executable compiled with out any extra flags
* segmentation_fault_with_debug : Executable compiled with with debug flags